      <link>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A7%92%E6%9D%80%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/03__%E4%BA%8C%E5%85%AB%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E6%9C%89%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%80%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A5%BD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A7%92%E6%9D%80%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/03__%E4%BA%8C%E5%85%AB%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E6%9C%89%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%80%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A5%BD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;假设你的系统中存储有几十亿上百亿的商品，而每天有千万级的商品被上亿的用户访问，那么肯定有一部分被大量用户访问的热卖商品，这就是我们常说的“热点商品”。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>04__流量削峰这事应该怎么做？</title>
      <link>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A7%92%E6%9D%80%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/04__%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E5%89%8A%E5%B3%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%8B%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%81%9A/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A7%92%E6%9D%80%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/04__%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E5%89%8A%E5%B3%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%8B%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%81%9A/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;如果你看过秒杀系统的流量监控图的话，你会发现它是一条直线，就在秒杀开始那一秒是一条很直很直的线，这是因为秒杀请求在时间上高度集中于某一特定的时间点。这样一来，就会导致一个特别高的流量峰值，它对资源的消耗是瞬时的。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>05__影响性能的因素有哪些？又该如何提高系统的性能？</title>
      <link>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A7%92%E6%9D%80%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/05__%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8F%88%E8%AF%A5%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD/</link>
